      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is in poor condition and needs some significant TLC, making it the perfect choice for a mechanic at heart or someone looking for a dedicated fixer-upper. It's a budget-friendly way to get started on your next automotive restoration journey and has plenty of potential for the right owner!",
      "price": 5500.0,
