    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in absolute pristine condition, featuring supple, unworn leather and that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and recent preventative maintenance. Every button, switch, and feature functions perfectly. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
